Knowledge is very influential with the teacher's skills regarding critical thinking. Based on Table 2, teachers' knowledge of critical thinking is good, with an average value of 3.4 and 3.3. From the results of this questionnaire, the knowledge and skills of teachers based on each critical thinking indicator have almost the same value. Elementary school teacher knowledge data about critical thinking is in Table 3.
